content:
Manage territories the same way you did by using Enterprise Territory Management, but now under the name Sales Territories. The new name better represents key disciplines for designing and managing territories as part of your teams’ overall efforts around sales performance management. And most importantly, Sales Territories isn’t just for enterprise businesses!

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.

Salesforce Help: Sales Territories
title: Enterprise Territory Management Changes to Sales Territories
